I am especially drawn to Piper Companies’ mission of helping clients build high-performing teams while connecting premier talent with exceptional opportunities, and to your focus on collaborative partnerships with predictable, measurable results. I would welcome the opportunity to contribute to that goal through reliable automation systems that improve operational outcomes. I can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration.

